Title: Back to Headquarters!
Description:
Eadweard called for your return to the main office after I'd finished with you... er, this experiment, I mean.

I'm sure it has to do with pomp, circumstance, reward, and what have you. If any of that entices you, then best hurry before his bag of goodies runs dry to all the other recent recruits.
ObjectivesText: Meet with Eadweard Dalyngrigge at Algeth'ar Academy in Thaldraszus.
